text: Rokia Doumbia (born 5 May 1999) is a Malian basketball player for Purdue Boilermakers and the Malian national team.Afrobasket.com profile She represented Mali at the 2019 Women's Afrobasket.2019 Women's Afrobasket profile ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Arkansas Razorbacks women's basketball players Category:Centers (basketball) Category:Malian women's basketball players Category:Purdue Boilermakers women's basketball players Category:Sportspeople from Bradenton, Florida
